# Chatbot Personality

The chatbot's system prompt is built from two text files at server startup:

1. **`src/data/chatbot-instructions.txt`** — behavioral instructions (tone, response style, hidden features like /match). Edit this to change how the chatbot acts.
2. **`src/data/resume-prompt.txt`** — resume content (auto-generated by `npm run update:resume`). Do not edit this directly; update the resume PDF instead.

`server.js` loads both files and combines them into a single system prompt. No code changes needed to tweak chatbot behavior.

## When the user wants to change chatbot behavior

1. Edit `src/data/chatbot-instructions.txt`
2. Run `npm test` to verify nothing broke
3. Report the changes made
